ðŸ“¦ pkg-info
===========

Tiny library to fetch package info from `PyPI <https://pypi.org/>`_.


Install
-------

``pipenv install pkg_info``

or

``pip install pkg_info``

Usage
-----

.. code-block:: python

    from pkg_info import get_pkg_info

    pkg = get_pkg_info('requests')
    pkg.name        # 'requests'
    pkg.version     # '2.18.4'
    pkg.author.name # 'Kenneth Reitz'

List of supported properties
----------------------------

.. code:: yaml

    name: str
    license: str
    summary: str
    description: str
    version: str
    keywords: str
    homepage: str
    url: str
    author:
      - name: str
      - email: str
    maintainer:
      - name: str
      - email: str


